    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Run rJava with RStudio under OSX 10.10]]></title>
    <link href="http://Powernap.github.io/blog/2015/02/20/run-rjava-with-rstudio-under-osx-10-dot-10/"/>
    <updated>2015-02-20T14:30:10+01:00</updated>
